      IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      PROGRAM-ID. CHRISTMAS-TREE.

      ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      FILE-CONTROL.
          SELECT TREE-FILE ASSIGN TO "christmastree.txt"
              ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.

      DATA DIVISION.
      FILE SECTION.
      FD TREE-FILE.
      01 TREE-LINE     PIC X(80).

      WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      01 NUM-TIMES     PIC 99 VALUE 0.
      01 EOF-FLAG      PIC X VALUE "N".

      PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      MAIN-LOGIC.
      DISPLAY "How many times? ".
      ACCEPT NUM-TIMES.
      PERFORM PRINT-CHRISTMAS-TREE NUM-TIMES TIMES.
      STOP RUN.

      PRINT-CHRISTMAS-TREE.
      OPEN INPUT TREE-FILE.
      MOVE "N" TO EOF-FLAG.
      PERFORM UNTIL EOF-FLAG = "Y"
          READ TREE-FILE
              AT END MOVE "Y" TO EOF-FLAG
              NOT AT END DISPLAY TREE-LINE
          END-READ
      END-PERFORM.
      CLOSE TREE-FILE.